36:49.701 --> 36:52.399
set on singing
during the ceremony!

36:52.400 --> 36:54.909
I don't want to be singing
as you're walking out!

36:54.910 --> 36:57.942
I want to have a special
moment with you girls!

36:58.009 --> 37:00.711
We girls have had lots of
special moments, Mother.

37:00.779 --> 37:01.979
You just weren't there.

37:02.047 --> 37:03.516
I resent that.

37:03.772 --> 37:05.251
And I also resent the fact

37:05.252 --> 37:07.374
that you are keeping
me in the background

37:07.375 --> 37:09.231
at my own daughter's
wedding, which,

37:09.232 --> 37:12.281
I am sorry to say I
still think is bizarre!

37:12.282 --> 37:15.349
You know when I finally
began to like who I am?

37:15.417 --> 37:17.084
When I stopped
trying to please you.

37:17.152 --> 37:20.187
So Jean and I had to learn
how to become our own family,

37:20.255 --> 37:23.324
and you can't just waltz
in here after all this time

37:23.392 --> 37:25.860
and start calling the shots.
You're a bully, Mother.

37:25.928 --> 37:27.194
It's taken till now to realize it,

37:27.262 --> 37:29.484
but you are a bully. I am not!

37:29.485 --> 37:32.333
Mother, I cannot remember
a conversation with you

37:32.401 --> 37:35.503
