feeling worse about myself.

37:35.571 --> 37:36.624
Well, you know what, Susan?

37:36.724 --> 37:39.040
I'm disappointed in you.

37:39.107 --> 37:39.826
I'm sorry to say, Mother,

37:39.827 --> 37:41.542
you are no longer
invited to my wedding.

37:41.610 --> 37:42.777
What about my song?

37:42.844 --> 37:44.879
You are welcome to sing
"The Sound of Silence"

37:44.947 --> 37:46.480
in your hotel room right now.

37:48.650 --> 37:50.117
All right.

37:55.891 --> 37:58.233
And to think I was
going to send you

37:58.234 --> 38:00.188
to Israel for your honeymoon.

38:00.388 --> 38:02.335
They love me there.

38:04.138 --> 38:05.971
You look beautiful.

38:06.673 --> 38:08.241
You're beautiful.

38:12.433 --> 38:13.232
Hi.

38:13.300 --> 38:15.161
Arnica twice a day.

38:15.261 --> 38:16.903
It'll help your bruise.

38:16.971 --> 38:18.805
Thanks.

38:18.872 --> 38:21.941
I've been thinking a lot
about what you did for Kurt.

38:22.009 --> 38:23.236
It made a real impact.

38:23.237 --> 38:25.013
I thought the only
impact that was made was

38:25.014 --> 38:27.413
Karofsky's fist impacting my face.

38:27.481 --> 38:29.382
You saw what Finn
did at the wedding.

38:29.450 --> 38:31.951
That was because of you.

38:32.019 --> 38:32.885
We've been talking
this whole time,

38:32.886 --> 38:35.955
and you haven't even noticed
that I'm wearing your ring.

38:37.124 --> 38:39.225
How'd you get that?

38:39.293 --> 38:41.027
I broke into your locker.

38:41.095 --> 38:43.696
I've always been really
handy with a nail file.

38:43.764 --> 38:45.465
Really? Mm-hmm.

38:55.943 --> 38:57.644
This is absolutely unacceptable.

38:57.711 --> 38:59.646
This psycho threatens
my kid's life,

38:59.713 --> 39:02.582
and some school board made up of
a bunch of people I've never met

39:02.650 --> 39:04.584
tells me there's nothing
they can do about it?

39:04.652 --> 39:06.085
Oh, they could do
something about it.

39:06.153 --> 39:07.320
They just decided not to.

39:07.388 --> 39:09.689
No one reported witnessing
him being violent,

39:09.757 --> 39:11.424
and there's no way to prove

39:11.492 --> 39:12.992
that he threatened
you with violence.

39:13.060 --> 39:14.661
The school board president
issued a verbal warning

39:14.728 --> 39:17.163
to Karofsky,
and that's where we stand.

39:17.231 --> 39:19.332
I can't go back to being
terrified all the time.

39:19.400 --> 39:21.434
I jump every time a
locker slams shut.

39:21.502 --> 39:23.036
I flinch whenever
I turn the corner.

39:23.103 --> 39:25.004
I don't feel safe at the school.

39:25.072 --> 39:27.774
Kids who bully, for the most part,

39:27.841 --> 39:29.208
have been bullied themselves.

39:29.276 --> 39:30.576
And I for one don't flatter myself

39:30.644 --> 39:32.745
that that behavior can change.

39:32.813 --> 39:35.048
Now this kid Karofsky isn't
gonna all of a sudden

39:35.115 --> 39:37.383
be nice to you,
and I won't stand by

39:37.451 --> 39:39.185
unable to do anything about it.

39:39.253 --> 39:43.189
Effective noon tomorrow,
Figgins is back in charge

39:43.257 --> 39:46.059
as I've tendered my resignation
as principal in protest.

39:46.126 --> 39:48.695
I can't help you behind that desk,

39:48.762 --> 39:51.130
but I can be an extra pair of
eyes out in those hallways.

39:51.198 --> 39:53.066
Someone ought to have your back.

39:53.133 --> 39:56.169
Besides, I miss my office.
This room smells weird.

39:56.236 --> 39:59.172
I can't shake the feeling that
I'm inhaling a lot of dead skin.

40:02.810 --> 40:05.712
Well, I guess I'll try to
enjoy the rest of the day,

40:05.779 --> 40:07.180
before the terror starts anew.

40:07.247 --> 40:08.748
I'll see you at home.

40:10.718 --> 40:13.386
Hey, Kurt. Wait up a second.
There's something

40:13.454 --> 40:15.033
