pay for the tuition.

40:57.034 --> 40:58.701
Kurt, you can't leave.

40:58.769 --> 41:00.303
What the hell, dude?

41:00.371 --> 41:02.272
How about you talk with
me about this first?

41:02.339 --> 41:05.441
I'm sorry, Finn, but there's
nothing to talk about.

41:05.509 --> 41:06.676
Karofsky's coming back tomorrow,

41:06.744 --> 41:08.511
